{"tid":1561,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"夜闌人靜既時候，你會唔會諗起前度？","createTime":"2016-11-25T16:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T17:48:54.000Z","uid":5042,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb63d034e0d3d9ebac5d655ffd6b3c9e6d51afc0","tid":1561,"uid":5042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"明明已經分開左年幾有多 <br />\n明明佢已經有新男朋友<br />\n點解我仲係放唔低？<br />\n係因為未遇到另一個鐘意既定還是係我唔甘心？<br />\n唔甘心失去左佢 <br />\n好多人都叫我放低 下個更可愛<br />\n但真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打們你地明唔明我個感受.."},{"pid":"3371989baf0af32afc1b4a19bc853c9cc4566862","tid":1561,"uid":4704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:57:25.000Z","msg":"因為下一個未出現 你不斷諗起都正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗等時間沖淡都無野幫到"},{"pid":"b8feb95d6e6d5db274b69188446d03d285312990","tid":1561,"uid":4428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:08:40.000Z","msg":"真心下一個人會幫到你"},{"pid":"020c45dc0478cb5bda51208b44d716d6b08a2f07","tid":1561,"uid":4217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:10:51.000Z","msg":"當前度對你做啲好撚賤既事既時候<br />\n你就輕鬆放低"},{"pid":"99de43f0a951eba29be018a811f870180d879f1e","tid":1561,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:12:22.000Z","msg":"上面講得岩<br />\n搵到第二個就搞掂"},{"pid":"2743116b4f2dcf50db33588fe950aee01d19fe77","tid":1561,"uid":13286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:17:40.000Z","msg":"有時下個未必更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d60ab0caa8a9c7e3a029b7949904b203998481","tid":1561,"uid":11725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"曾經對一個女仔瘋狂過，自此不敢再動情，你唯一可以做嘅，就係唔好忘記。"},{"pid":"2ea2481a3d13c83059c90fd04d80fded9148d