dBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:28:20.000Z","msg":"講更散左之後拍左二次拖 拍個陣會係咁諗起佢<br />\n直到呢家單身 有時候好自然會諗<br />\n已經過左六年 我仲係放唔低 即使係拍左二個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係個陣同班一齊上堂啲記憶真係好刻骨銘心"},{"pid":"f2b3bdd47cb1dd0f2def9f55fe589accfd008982","tid":1561,"uid":10504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNZJMbfZExxG4z9m673pZXvViw16aJxQpMnnYM85BbuLo?filename=3kPtGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kPtGY.jpg&h=ff4e9cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以為搵一個新可以忘記到 但根本唔得 究竟係對愛情無信心 定係重未忘記到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4105f05abb5420b2770ab402a898f6c9d8b939e3","tid":1561,"uid":17133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"何必折磨自己呢。<br />\n搵其他嘢做分散下注意力啦"},{"pid":"3ecb9470db8c7c58341801ff35762a87883ba06c","tid":1561,"uid":20047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:56:07.000Z","msg":"係，無人幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d89dbf67bc57c850b3c82be68e5863a7e8150ce","tid":1561,"uid":84,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"咁實會㗎"},{"pid":"09c6def734efe9b122e40ee9dda483d24db42b48","tid":1561,"uid":22312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T06:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當前度對你做啲好撚賤既事既時候<br />\n你就輕鬆放低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢對我好差好差我都仲放唔低 唉"},{"pid":"a9ec03026a38fdde497e99f8bcda67826351b67c","tid":1561,"uid":5042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係，無人幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點會無人幫到你呀 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcce7a229789e6a1fefb6d65d2a20d355579ea6","tid":1561,"uid":5042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:05:27.000Z","msg":"其實個時都係自己唔好 <br />\n自己無安全感又逼到佢太緊<br />\n當初順其自然應該唔會搞到今日咁<br />\n應承佢會考既野我考到了<br />\n但佢已經唔係我身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56756636328e990ca42a23cee4bf7770d7510fb0","tid":1561,"uid":22652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:06:58.000Z","msg":"女人要用女人忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad8b0b90117746442f4c4c31b3e1aeae591ec83","tid":1561,"uid":7422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:12:00.000Z","msg":"我明 真係好難忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上年聖誕仲有佢係身邊 今年佢就同第二個一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65353410b69a18884673a683ba5455f95caf3ecb","tid":1561,"uid":21103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當前度對你做啲好撚賤既事既時候<br />\n你就輕鬆放低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚賤 但都會諗起佢 我係咪賤撚過狗"},{"pid":"8e3ce47510f7ffc76115333c580bb12e58137d38","tid":1561,"uid":22875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"分開了四年，感覺好似岩岩分開..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不時諗起佢"},{"pid":"3b1bc6b5c5cbfbc27a4d5d621cb2c5e3c5f4ce2d","tid":1561,"uid":5042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"想知道你是否還是一樣<br />\n有回來故事會不會是這樣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日覺得 再遇唔到一個自己會咁鐘意既女仔 sad"},{"pid":"838be6f69863f7682b6d66bec68505321a4b9a76","tid":1561,"uid":12320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"係咪只要同第二個拍拖就可以忘記到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68330256861fe34c6c803427084a272f2d559686","tid":1561,"uid":7422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪只要同第二個拍拖就可以忘記到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣做只會傷到第二個 冇謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b058ed88488331c6647bc016d4528a0a94e854","tid":1561,"uid":8937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經對一個女仔瘋狂過，自此不敢再動情，你唯一可以做嘅，就係唔好忘記。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e5caed87c3e56f0ab23d49ab87f16e4ebfe0ac","tid":1561,"uid":24007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T09:48:45.000Z","msg":"Focus做其他野，唔一定得但至少有幫助<br />\n<br />\n利申：做緊"},{"pid":"9936e5329eb729321533f00a67a04a95a26bb440","tid":1561,"uid":5042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪只要同第二個拍拖就可以忘記到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣做只會傷到第二個 冇謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講得岩 我要等自己有日完全放低曬<br />\n又或者遇到第二個咁鐘意既先會再拍拖<br />\n唔係對另一個好唔公平"},{"pid":"f3e79c6dbc9ca417a16e8494c0d87db870136ce7","tid":1561,"uid":5042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:04:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Focus做其他野，唔一定得但至少有幫助<br />\n<br />\n利申：做緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過搵好多好多野做去麻醉自己 <br />\n令到自己好攰 <br />\n但一夜晚 靜 訓唔著既時候又會諗起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22291ed79377453474f5224adcf3a95a1a08385","tid":1561,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"會 但已經放低左 大家都已經有新歡 諗起嘅都係之前開心嘅事 明白過左去就過左去 有時吾適合就係吾適合 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱散個時喊到隻狗咁"},{"pid":"90c12b956b8e0343b2243ec2f83495700fc55e3a","tid":1561,"uid":5042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會 但已經放低左 大家都已經有新歡 諗起嘅都係之前開心嘅事 明白過左去就過左去 有時吾適合就係吾適合 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱散個時喊到隻狗咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過 係張床睇返啲對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32db30161cd907c6d29e64eeb9bd6fc8db5e943c","tid":1561,"uid":23909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T12:26:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會 但已經放低左 大家都已經有新歡 諗起嘅都係之前開心嘅事 明白過左去就過左去 有時吾適合就係吾適合 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱散個時喊到隻狗咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過 係張床睇返啲對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實真係好睇你點諗 我係上一秒仲諗吾通好掛住佢 但一知道佢係我死下死下嘅時候係到講我壞話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲同我本身嘅朋友fd埋一齊講我 (散個幾日同班fd炒埋) 下一秒就覺得好彩呢個人吾要我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後來有而家呢個男朋友先知佢暗戀左我好耐 有幾年 即使冇之前拍拖嘅激情都會覺得好安心好穩定 sor講多左 簡單一句就係 等下一個同埋要自己識諗 留起美好嘅嘅就得喇"}]}